308
00:17:20,280 --> 00:17:21,079
Let’s go.

309
00:17:21,480 --> 00:17:22,200
Fast.

310
00:17:24,000 --> 00:17:25,359
Go quickly.

311
00:17:25,640 --> 00:17:27,240
I’m going to shower with my boyfriend, Saint.

312
00:17:27,560 --> 00:17:28,440
See you, bro.

313
00:17:28,760 --> 00:17:30,000
Go fast.

