317
00:18:16,040 --> 00:18:17,680
My heart loves it.

318
00:18:18,280 --> 00:18:20,000
Are you addicted to alcohol?

319
00:18:21,880 --> 00:18:22,840
Not addicted to alcohol.

320
00:18:23,720 --> 00:18:25,200
