327
00:20:19,360 --> 00:20:20,440
Hello.

328
00:20:21,000 --> 00:20:21,880
Who is this?

329
00:20:22,200 --> 00:20:22,920
It’s me.

330
00:20:23,240 --> 00:20:24,040
Saint.

331
00:20:25,560 --> 00:20:27,000
